<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Stablecoins & Payments – Track 3 – Cointist Guides</title>
  <style>
:root{
  --bg:#0b0d10; --ink:#e7edea; --muted:#9aa7a7;
  --card:#11151a; --border:#1e2630; --pill:#1a2027;
  --accent:#2ce561; --gold:#e6c679; --shadow:0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.35);
}
*{box-sizing:border-box}
body{margin:0;background:var(--bg);color:var(--ink);
  font:16px/1.65 system-ui,-apple-system,"SF Pro Text","SF Pro Display",Segoe UI,Roboto,Arial,sans-serif}
.hero{border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(230,198,121,.06),rgba(44,229,97,.03))}
.hero-inner{max-width:1120px;margin:0 auto;padding:28px 20px}
.crumbs{color:var(--muted);font-size:13px;margin-bottom:10px}
.crumbs a{color:var(--muted);text-decoration:none}
.crumbs span{opacity:.6;margin:0 .4rem}
.hero h1{font-size:34px;margin:0 0 8px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--gold),var(--accent));-webkit-background-clip:text;background-clip:text;color:transparent}
.hero .meta{display:flex;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap;color:#cfd8d5;font-size:13px}
.kpi{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;background:var(--pill);border:1px solid var(--border);padding:4px 10px;border-radius:999px}
.wrap{max-width:1120px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 20px}
.grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:minmax(0,1fr) 300px;gap:28px;align-items:start}
@media (max-width:1060px){.grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
.definition{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;padding:16px 18px;box-shadow:var(--shadow);margin:22px 0}
.definition h3{margin:0 0 8px;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.12em;color:#b6c4c0}
.definition p{margin:0;color:#e9f3ef}
article{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:16px;padding:24px;box-shadow:var(--shadow)}
h2{margin:22px 0 10px;font-size:24px}
h3{margin:16px 0 8px;font-size:18px}
p{margin:12px 0}
ul,ol{margin:10px 0 10px 18px}
.divider{height:1px;background:var(--border);margin:22px 0}
.callout{border-left:3px solid var(--accent);background:#0f1419;border:1px solid var(--border);padding:12px 14px;border-radius:8px;color:#dfe8e4}
.table{overflow:auto} table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse}
th,td{border:1px solid var(--border);padding:10px 12px;text-align:left}
code{background:#0e1318;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;padding:2px 6px}
.related{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;padding:16px;margin-top:24px}
.chips{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px}
.chip{display:inline-block;padding:6px 10px;border-radius:999px;background:var(--pill);border:1px solid var(--border);font-size:13px;color:#cfe7d8;text-decoration:none}
.toc{position:sticky;top:24px;background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;padding:16px;box-shadow:var(--shadow)}
.toc h4{margin:0 0 10px;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:.08em;color:#c9d6d2}
.toc ol{margin:0;padding-left:18px}
.toc a{color:#e7f4ef;text-decoration:none}
.toc a:hover{border-bottom:1px dashed var(--accent)}
.note{color:#8aa399;font-size:12px;margin-top:14px}


/* Track 3 KPI bar */
.kpi-bar{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px;margin:10px 0 6px 0}
.kpi-pill{
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;
  padding:10px 12px;border-radius:999px;
  border:1px solid var(--border);
  position:relative; overflow:hidden;
  background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(41,246,161,.08), rgba(44,229,97,.04));
}
.kpi-pill::before{
  content:""; position:absolute; inset:0;
  background:linear-gradient(90deg, #29f6a133, #2ce56122);
  pointer-events:none;
}
.kpi-ico{
  width:12px;height:12px;border-radius:3px;
  background:linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent-2), var(--accent));
  box-shadow:0 0 10px rgba(44,229,97,.35);
}
.kpi-text{font-size:13px;color:#e6f4ee}
.kpi-sub{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted)}
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <div class="crumbs">Track 3 · <a href="/education/applications">Applications</a></div>
      <h1>Stablecoins & Payments</h1>
      <div class="meta">
        <span class="kpi">Intermediate</span>
        <span class="kpi">8–12 min read</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
<article>
  <aside class="definition"><h3>DEFINITION</h3><p>Stablecoins target price stability (usually $1) and power low-friction payments. Designs include fiat-backed, crypto-collateralized, and algorithmic/hybrid models.</p></aside>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <h2 id="designs">Designs</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Fiat-backed: off-chain reserves, attestation cadence, redeemability.</li>
    <li>Crypto-collateralized: on-chain reserves, overcollateralization, liquidation engines.</li>
    <li>Algorithmic/hybrid: supply rules + collateral; higher design risk.</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <h2 id="payments">Payments rails</h2>
  <p>On/off-ramps, merchant acceptance, L2 fees/latency, and compliance endpoints (KYC/AML, travel rule).</p>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <h2 id="metrics">Metrics & KPIs</h2>
  <div class="kpi-bar">
<div class="kpi-pill">
  <span class="kpi-ico" aria-hidden="true"></span>
  <div>
    <div class="kpi-text"><strong>Peg deviation</strong></div>
    <div class="kpi-sub">Median price vs $1 over time</div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="kpi-pill">
  <span class="kpi-ico" aria-hidden="true"></span>
  <div>
    <div class="kpi-text"><strong>Redeemability</strong></div>
    <div class="kpi-sub">Mint/burn windows and frictions</div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="kpi-pill">
  <span class="kpi-ico" aria-hidden="true"></span>
  <div>
    <div class="kpi-text"><strong>Reserve quality</strong></div>
    <div class="kpi-sub">Asset mix, duration, transparency</div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="kpi-pill">
  <span class="kpi-ico" aria-hidden="true"></span>
  <div>
    <div class="kpi-text"><strong>On-chain velocity</strong></div>
    <div class="kpi-sub">Tx volume / circulating supply</div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="kpi-pill">
  <span class="kpi-ico" aria-hidden="true"></span>
  <div>
    <div class="kpi-text"><strong>Acceptance</strong></div>
    <div class="kpi-sub">Merchants & wallets that support it</div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="kpi-pill">
  <span class="kpi-ico" aria-hidden="true"></span>
  <div>
    <div class="kpi-text"><strong>Settlement cost</strong></div>
    <div class="kpi-sub">Avg fee & time-to-finality</div>
  </div>
</div>
</div>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <h2 id="ops">Operational notes</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Plan for chain outages or L2 sequencer downtime.</li>
    <li>Monitor bridge/liquidity fragmentation across chains.</li>
  </ul>

